># through_via / blind_via disallow keywords were master-only relative to
#^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ source.kicad-dru comment.line.number-sign.kicad-dru
># KiCad 9 but shipped in KiCad 10.0.0; verified against the 10.0.0 tag
